&lt;p>​I was the Development Director of AVSpec from 2016 - 2018, developing the concept, backend, and frontend of the the database. I was supported in this role by the 2016 &amp;amp; 2017 Margaret Mayall Fellowships.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>The site is now live: &lt;a href="www.aavso.org/apps/specdb">www.aavso.org/apps/specdb&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
